/*===========================================================================
FUNCTION cmss_get_cdma_ecio

DESCRIPTION
  This function gets the CDMA ECIO from searcher

DEPENDENCIES
  Phone is in the digital mode

RETURNS
  negative Ec/IO value in 0.5 dBm steps.

SIDE EFFECTS
  none

===========================================================================*/
